documentType: evidence inventory and chain of custody form
summary: This is an FBI evidence inventory and chain of custody form (FD-1087) for a box of evidence collected on August 28, 2006, related to case 31E-MM-108062. The box contains various white papers and messages, some with initials, and a Jet Blue receipt. The document shows evidence handling and inventory updates through July 2021.

events.title: Evidence Collection
events.description: A box of evidence was collected, containing various white papers, messages, and a Jet Blue receipt, as part of case 31E-MM-108062.

events.title: Last Inventory
events.description: The evidence was last inventoried, as recorded on the form.

keyFacts: Evidence was collected on August 28, 2006, for case 31E-MM-108062, which is likely related to the Epstein investigation.
The evidence box contained a Jet Blue receipt and numerous white papers and messages, some referenced by initials (e.g., J.L., D.M., M.H., J.S., H.S., G., S.).
The evidence was held by the FBI New York office and later noted as being in Miami, with chain of custody and inventory updates through July 2021.
The document is an official FBI evidence form (FD-1087) detailing the items seized and their handling.
